Paper: hep-th/9606095

Date: 1996-06-17

Title: Bosonization of vertex operators for the $A^{(1)_{n-1}$ face model

Authors: Y. Asai, M. Jimbo, T. Miwa and Y. Pugai

Journal-ref: J.Phys. A29 (1996) 6595-6616

We present a free boson realization of the vertex operators and their dualsfor the solvable SOS lattice model of $A^{(1)}_{n-1}$ type. We discuss apossible connection to the calculation of the correlation functions.